ation will be inhibited\nand the cloud fragments. The cooling time of the environment within which the\ncloud is embedded is however very long: thus, star formation from the\nfragmented cloud remains strongly inhibited.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jun 2008 17:08:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Jul 2008 10:13:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
