 the overall rate of the formation of complex molecules such\nas methanol which require successive hydrogenation on the grain surfaces in the\ninterstellar medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Jun 2008 11:46:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-06-30"}
